Put @boneless skinless chicken thighs{8} on sheet pan (no need to cut)
Cut @red onion{1} into thick slices and put on sheet pan
Cut @broccoli{2%heads} into bite-size pieces
Add @mango chutney{2%jars} on top of the onion, broccoli, and chicken thighs
Sprinkle @masala curry powder{1%tbsp} on top
Serve with @jasmine rice{2%cups} (follow instructions on package to cook)
